laboratory_examinations.findings: Hypoplastic right internal carotid artery, hypoplastic middle cerebral arteries, and a dysplastic basilar artery.
Images of the facial hemangioma obtained; embolization performed.
Successful embolization of most of the facial hemangioma.
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: Rapid involution of the hemangioma with a clinically apparent progressive decrease in size within the 6 weeks after the embolization.
